6b:["$","$L75",null,{"districtName":"Kozhikode to Wayanad","serviceLabel":"One Way Taxi","faqs":[{"question":"What is the taxi fare from Kozhikode to Wayanad?","answer":"The one-way taxi fare from Kozhikode to Wayanad starts at ₹1190 for a hatchback (₹13/km × 85 km). Sedan fare: ~₹1190. SUV/Innova: ~₹1615. All fares include driver bata, tolls, permits, and GST."},{"question":"How far is Kozhikode from Wayanad by taxi?","answer":"The distance from Kozhikode to Wayanad by road is approximately 85 km. The taxi journey takes about 1h 33m depending on traffic and route conditions."},{"question":"Is one-way taxi available from Kozhikode to Wayanad?","answer":"Yes! OneWayTaxi.ai offers one-way taxi service from Kozhikode to Wayanad starting at just ₹1190. You pay only for the one-way distance — no return charges. Book online or call us 24/7 at +91 81244 76010."},{"question":"What types of cabs are available for Kozhikode to Wayanad?","answer":"We offer multiple vehicle types for the Kozhikode to Wayanad route: Mini/Hatchback (4 seats, ₹13/km), Sedan (4 seats, ₹14/km), SUV (7 seats, ₹19/km), and Innova Crysta (7 seats, ₹22/km). All vehicles are AC and GPS-tracked."},{"question":"Can I book a Kozhikode to Wayanad taxi for early morning or late night?","answer":"Yes, our Kozhikode to Wayanad taxi service is available 24/7, 365 days a year — including early mornings, late nights, weekends, and holidays. Book at any time through our website or call +91 81244 76010."},{"question":"Is the Kozhikode to Wayanad taxi fare fixed or metered?","answer":"Our Kozhikode to Wayanad taxi fare is fixed and pre-booked. The fare you see at booking is what you pay — no meter, no surge pricing, no hidden charges. All inclusive of tolls, driver bata, and GST."}]}]
